Whether fueled by mental illness, irrational anger, pure unadulterated hate or a combination of those things, these attacks capped off a truly hideous year in America.
Also in 2018, there were 1,879 incidents of anti-Semitism, according to the Anti-Defamation League.
The rise in hate in America is hard to ignore.
In response to my request to “put down our politics and find a cure” for the sickness of hate, I got mostly political clap-backs.
They have to put down their politics, first.”Inarguably, politics is a part of our hate problem.